## Step 3: vm.ts — Resource Limit (limit annotation 집행)

### 3-1: Frame에 resourceLimits 추가

```typescript
type Frame = {
  retAddr: number; baseSlot: number; fn: string; upvalues: Value[];
  capabilities: Array<{cap: string; arg?: string}>;
  resourceLimits: { cpu?: number; memory?: number; io?: number };  // ← 추가
  opCount: number;  // 실행된 opcode 수
};
```

### 3-2: compileFnBody 에서 limit annotations → resourceLimits 추출

compiler.ts의 compileFnBody에 limit 처리 추가:
```typescript
const resourceLimits: Record<string, number> = {}
annotations
  .filter((a: any) => a.kind === "limit")
  .forEach((a: any) => { resourceLimits[a.resource] = a.value })
// fn Value에 resourceLimits도 저장
addConst({ tag: "fn", ..., capabilities, resourceLimits })
```

### 3-3: Op.Call에서 Frame에 resourceLimits 전달

```typescript
this.frames.push({
  ...,
  capabilities: callee.capabilities || [],
  resourceLimits: (callee as any).resourceLimits || {},
  opCount: 0,
});
